{"article_id":"VlwdI7caZ7dRyQno","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senator who the president derides with a racist nickname","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"has a book","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to promote ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"a seat","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to win","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and rumors of a White House bid","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to ...","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"neither confirm nor deny","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Donald Trump has named his most likely challenger in the 2020 presidential election .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"It is Elizabeth Warren .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"100 daze of Trump :","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"euphoria and nausea on the White House rollercoaster","depth":3},{"id":12,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":13,"text":"Standing before the faithful of the National Rifle Association in Atlanta on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"the president predicted a surfeit of candidates .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" You ' ll have plenty of those Democrats","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"coming over","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"and you ' re going to say ,","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"' No , sir , no thank you -","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"no , ma ' am , ' \"","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"the president said .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"\" Perhaps ma ' am .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"It may be Pocahontas ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"remember that . \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Pocahontas is the racially charged term","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that Trump used on the campaign trail","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"to dismiss Warren ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"who has claimed Native American heritage .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Clearly , she had got under his skin .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"The Massachusetts senator was a self-declared \" nasty woman \" with a message for Trump :","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" Women have had it with guys like you. \"","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"She went toe to toe with him on his favourite medium , Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"hammering him","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"for delivering a \" one-two punch of bigotry and economic lies \" .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"It is small wonder that ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"if asked who now personifies the anti-Trump resistance ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Warren would come top of many people ' s lists .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"At 67 , the former Harvard law professor is a formidable figure with a reputation for reticence","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"bordering on aloofness","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"when approached by reporters in the corridors of Capitol Hill .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"But the woman","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"who walks into Senate Democratic offices in Washington for this interview ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"wearing a blue jacket and dark trousers ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"is the opposite of aloof .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"\" Elizabeth Warren , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"she says ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"despite being instantly recognisable to anyone","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"following US politics ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"offering a handshake and warm smile .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"She reminisces about her first visit to this room ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"when she was on her way to becoming a senator in 2012 ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and jokes about ' s voice recorder resembling a Taser .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"when she turns to business ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"she is characteristically forthright","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and makes clear","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that Barack Obama ' s grace period","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"- a presidential afterglow","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"in which he is beyond criticism in the Democratic party -","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"is over .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Most Americans are being left behind in this economy .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Worse than being left behind ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"they ' re getting kicked in the teeth","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"\" I think","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"President Obama , like many others in both parties , talks about a set of big national statistics","depth":16},{"id":65,"text":"that look shiny and great","depth":17},{"id":66,"text":"but increasingly have giant blind spots , \"","depth":17},{"id":67,"text":"she says .","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"\" That GDP , unemployment , no longer reflect the lived experiences of most Americans .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"And the lived experiences of most Americans is that they are being left behind in this economy .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"\" Worse than being left behind ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"they ' re getting kicked in the teeth . \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"In the topsy-turvy election , both Trump and the leftwing candidate for the Democratic nomination , Bernie Sanders , spoke of a rigged economy .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Hillary Clinton , the Democratic nominee , has articulated the view","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that Obama did not get the credit","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"he deserved","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"from rescuing America from the financial crisis of 2007-08 .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"That ,","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"it transpired ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"was small comfort to voters in decaying industrial towns","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"who felt","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"the globalisation train had left the station without them .","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"With Sanders still a leading voice and energy","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"coming from the progressive base ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"and centrist politics around the world in retreat ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"it might be tempting for the Democrats to turn left .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Warren","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"-","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"who grew up in deep red Oklahoma","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"but now lives in Massachusetts , the state of the Kennedys -","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"frames the question in a different way .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Again , she demonstrates a willingness","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"to criticise her own party .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"\" I think","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"left-right is less and less an accurate description of the political landscape , \"","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"she says .","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"\" Now , having said that ,","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"I think","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"there are real differences between the Republicans and the Democrats here in the United States .","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"The Republicans have clearly thrown their lot in with the rich and the powerful ,","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"but so have a lot of Democrats .","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"You know ,","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"it ' s a question","depth":16},{"id":103,"text":"of walking the walk on working people , on fighting for working people .","depth":16},{"id":104,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"that was the real point . \"","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"Warren did not not name any individuals .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Some commentators have criticised Bill and Hillary Clinton for becoming too close to wealthy elites .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"Much has been written in the electoral postmortems over the definition of a Democrat :","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"whether economic populism was neglected during the election in favour of identity politics","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"relating to gender , race and sexuality .","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"For progressives , it might be argued that Warren represents the best of Clinton and Sanders","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"rolled into one :","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"strong on issues such as equal pay and reproductive rights","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"but equally strong on class inequality and economic opportunity .","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"This is also what makes her such a tempting target for Trump and the Republicans .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"\" I think","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"it ' s a false choice , \"","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"she says .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"\" To talk about the economics of survival in the 21st century is also to include a woman ' s right","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"to make decisions over her own body , a woman ' s meaningful access to birth control .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"That is as deeply woven into the economic stability of that woman individually , her family , her community , this entire nation .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"those are deeply tied to each other .","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"Not either-ors . \"","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"The senator ' s choice of abortion as an example is timely .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Sanders triggered fierce soul searching in the party last week","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"by rallying in Omaha , Nebraska for a mayoral candidate","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"who opposes abortion rights","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"but promises economic justice .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Pro-choice activists described it as a betrayal of the women","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"who have been in the vanguard of the resistance to Trump .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Would Warren endorse a Democratic candidate","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"who was anti-abortion ?","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"\" Probably not , \"","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"she says .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"\" But let me be clear .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Look ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"I ' m pro-choice ,","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"I ' m strongly pro-choice ,","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"I ' ve been in these fights forever and forever and forever","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"and at the federal level this is powerfully important to me ...","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"I get","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"that not everyone in the Democratic party agrees with me","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"but I am in this fight all the way . \"","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"Trump has energised and galvanised the apathetic and apolitical .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"He made politics great again in the sense","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"of getting people to care","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"instead of allowing it to hum softly in the background .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Suddenly , it is no longer a tepid struggle within the grey managerial class .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Suddenly it matters .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Newspaper readership and news channel viewership have revived after years of decline ;","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"late-night TV comedians are thriving .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"What Trump Did Next is a constant topic of conversation at dinner tables .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"It may yet prove to be his legacy .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Many call Trump a fascist .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"100 days in , is he just a reactionary Republican ? |","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"Victoria de Grazia","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":159,"text":"On 21 January , for example , more than 400,000 protesters took part in a women ' s march in Washington ,","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"with millions more marching across America and around the world .","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"For Warren , it was an awakening :","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"when the history of this time period is written","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"it will be about Donald Trump ' s election ,","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"no doubt ,","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"but it will be about the Women ' s March","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"the day","depth":14},{"id":169,"text":"after Donald Trump was inaugurated .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"Democracy changed in America on that day . \"","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"We are no longer a country","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"that believes","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"we can do politics only once every four years , or even once every two years ,","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"no longer a country","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"that says","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"that democracy is only about elections","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"and that it will tend to itself in the time periods between elections .","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"People are deeply engaged in issues right now .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"The healthcare fight .","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"Immigration . \"","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"Warren advocates marches and rallies , online protests , viral videos , collective action and running for office .","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"\" Let me give a giant hug to the resistance .","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"Resistance , persistence , insistence","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"- every part of it -","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"and how to bring more people into the fight .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Look ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"Democrats are in the minority in the House , in the Senate ,","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"our tools are very limited","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"to block Trump ' s actions","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"but democracy is working in an entirely new way .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"\" This is one of the things","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"I now talk about","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"everywhere we go ,","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"about how to get more engaged","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"and how people can make their voices more effective ,","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"and how they can make sure","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"they get heard in Washington ,","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"and it is changing the United States Congress .","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"Not fast enough ,","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"but it ' s changing it . \"","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"Trump has tried to undermine a free press .","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"He ' s shown no respect for the courts .","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"Those are the steps","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"authoritarians take","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"Warren , a mother of two and grandmother of three , is at the tip of that particular spear .","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"She has never met Trump","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"- the closest","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"she came","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"was at the inauguration -","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"but she clashed with him on Twitter last year .","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"\" Thumbs at 30 paces , \"","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"she jokes ,","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"miming the typing action in mid-air .","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"On 21 March 2016 , she posted :","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"\" Many of history ' s worst authoritarians started out as losers","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"- and @ realDonaldTrump is a serious threat. \"","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"In her new book , This Fight is Our Fight , she recalls on inauguration day seeing protesters","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"carrying a giant banner","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"that said just one word :","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"\" FASCIST . \"","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"Asked if she considers Trump an authoritarian , a fascist ,","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"she replies forcefully :","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"\" Look at what he has done .","depth":11},{"id":224,"text":"He has expressed his admiration for Mussolini , for Vladimir Putin .","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"He has tried to undermine a free press .","depth":14},{"id":226,"text":"He ' s shown no respect for the courts .","depth":14},{"id":227,"text":"Those are the steps","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"that authoritarians take .","depth":14},{"id":229,"text":"\" Can America withstand it ? \"","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"That ' s ultimately what the book is about .","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"It ' s the narrative arc","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"of how America built a middle class","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"and then corporate CEOs and billionaires took the legs out from underneath the middle class ,","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"how their tool was money ,","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"and the final chapter , whether or not we can withstand the punch","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"that Donald Trump delivers to our working families and to our democracy .","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"And yet ,","depth":8},{"id":238,"text":"I would say ,","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"this book ends on a note of optimism .","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"\" Trump may be a one-off","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"but the conditions","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"that produced him","depth":10},{"id":243,"text":"are not .","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"The disillusionment in towns across America","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"that felt forgotten by flashy big cities ,","depth":12},{"id":246,"text":"that felt","depth":13},{"id":247,"text":"they had nothing to lose","depth":14},{"id":248,"text":"by voting for Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":249,"text":"rhymed with what led to the Brexit vote in the UK .","depth":10},{"id":250,"text":"America had Reagan and trickle-down economics ;","depth":10},{"id":251,"text":"Britain had Thatcher and the invisible hand of the market .","depth":10},{"id":252,"text":"\" There are certainly parallels , \"","depth":10},{"id":253,"text":"Warren says .","depth":10},{"id":254,"text":"\" Billionaires and corporate CEOs have figured out","depth":12},{"id":255,"text":"that for an investment of millions of dollars - they can get returns of billions of dollars .","depth":12},{"id":256,"text":"So","depth":12},{"id":257,"text":"if they can get their snout to the trough of government money , government handouts , government gifts , government loopholes ,","depth":13},{"id":258,"text":"they can get richer and richer and richer .","depth":13},{"id":259,"text":"It ' s not a secret","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"that was developed here in the United States alone .","depth":12},{"id":261,"text":"It ' s a point","depth":12},{"id":262,"text":"that ' s spread all around the globe . \"","depth":12},{"id":263,"text":"In This Fight is Our Fight , Warren recalls a conversation with her husband , Bruce Mann ,","depth":8},{"id":264,"text":"over whether to run for president in 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":265,"text":"He pointed out","depth":10},{"id":266,"text":"how difficult the first Senate race was .","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"\" It was hard for him to see me ridiculed and called names ,","depth":11},{"id":268,"text":"hard to see our children dragged into political attacks ,","depth":12},{"id":269,"text":"hard to see both his sister and my brothers worry , \"","depth":12},{"id":270,"text":"she writes .","depth":10},{"id":271,"text":"He gave her his blessing","depth":9},{"id":272,"text":"but talking it through with him decided her against .","depth":9},{"id":273,"text":"Trump 's promise for healthcare act contradicts Republicans ' proposal","depth":8},{"id":274,"text":"Read more","depth":8},{"id":275,"text":"Will this deter her again in 2020 ?","depth":11},{"id":276,"text":"Clinton recently said","depth":12},{"id":277,"text":"she believes","depth":13},{"id":278,"text":"misogyny played a part in her own defeat .","depth":13},{"id":279,"text":"Reviewing Warren ' s book for the New York Times ,","depth":12},{"id":280,"text":"economist Paul Krugman wrote :","depth":12},{"id":281,"text":"\" Let ' s be honest :","depth":12},{"id":282,"text":"Republicans have gone after Warren herself , in a way","depth":14},{"id":283,"text":"they haven ' t gone after Sanders ,","depth":14},{"id":284,"text":"in part because of her gender . \"","depth":13},{"id":285,"text":"Warren does not say no .","depth":9},{"id":286,"text":"But first ,","depth":11},{"id":287,"text":"she reminds us ,","depth":11},{"id":288,"text":"she has a Senate race","depth":11},{"id":289,"text":"to run in 2018 - a midterm election","depth":12},{"id":290,"text":"that should provide a clue as to the durability of the resistance at the ballot box .","depth":12},{"id":291,"text":"\" I said","depth":12},{"id":292,"text":"I ' m in this fight ,","depth":13},{"id":293,"text":"there ' s no pause about that , \"","depth":13},{"id":294,"text":"she says .","depth":11},{"id":295,"text":"\" I can take whatever somebody wants to throw at me .","depth":12},{"id":296,"text":"It ' s harder","depth":14},{"id":297,"text":"when things get thrown at your family","depth":14},{"id":298,"text":"but that ' s become the reality of 21st-century politics . \"","depth":13},{"id":299,"text":"She recalls her own journey , from janitor ' s daughter to Harvard academic to senator , thanks to opportunities","depth":14},{"id":300,"text":"she believes","depth":16},{"id":301,"text":"were lost to today ' s children","depth":16},{"id":302,"text":"when Washington decided","depth":16},{"id":303,"text":"it was more important to give tax breaks to billionaires and giant corporations .","depth":16},{"id":304,"text":"\" So that ' s what drives me , \"","depth":14},{"id":305,"text":"she says , passionately .","depth":14},{"id":306,"text":"\" And","depth":13},{"id":307,"text":"if you told me","depth":14},{"id":308,"text":"that what it would take for me","depth":17},{"id":309,"text":"to make a difference","depth":17},{"id":310,"text":"would be to get up every day","depth":17},{"id":311,"text":"and walk across broken glass","depth":17},{"id":312,"text":"but that I have a chance","depth":17},{"id":313,"text":"to open some doors for the next kid","depth":